<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>Udp - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/udp/</link><description>Udp - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/udp/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>TCP vs UDP</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/tcp%E4%B8%8Eudp/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/%E7%BD%91%E7%BB%9C%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE/tcp%E4%B8%8Eudp/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="tcp-vs-udp">TCP vs UDP</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：TCP通过三次握手、重传机制和流量控制实现可靠传输，适合数据完整性要求高的场景；UDP无连接、低延迟，适合实时性要求高于可靠性的场景。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="tcp通过连接管理和拥塞控制实现可靠传输udp以无连接和最小开销换取低延迟">TCP通过连接管理和拥塞控制实现可靠传输，UDP以无连接和最小开销换取低延迟</h2>
<h3 id="tcp核心机制可靠传输的三重保障">TCP核心机制：可靠传输的三重保障</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>机制</th>
          <th>解决的问题</th>
          <th>实现方式</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>连接管理</td>
          <td>端到端通信确认</td>
          <td>三次握手建立、四次挥手关闭</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>确认重传</td>
          <td>丢包恢复</td>
          <td>ACK确认 + 超时重传 + 快速重传</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>流量控制</td>
          <td>接收方处理不过来</td>
          <td>滑动窗口（rwnd）</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>拥塞控制</td>
          <td>网络拥塞</td>
          <td>慢启动、拥塞避免、快重传、快恢复</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<p><strong>三次握手（建立连接）</strong>：</p>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
